  "text": "Economics research on the usage of social media in organizations has supported the importance of managing and balancing the costs (e.g., privacy, enhanced expectations) and benefits (e.g., improved efficiency of business processes, knowledge sharing) of social media usage [CITATION_1] . A further operation that required balance in the NPD role was attendance at the training or competition environment.",
